title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Oct 31 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Oct 31 2022
description:
NBC News analyst blames Trump for mentally ill Pelosi attacker. Biden: Talk produces violence. Clay and Buck's Halloween plans. Senator Rand Paul joins Clay and Buck to discuss the left's double standard on political violence, the danger of allowing government to regulate speech and the key Senate races to watch. Colorado Senate candidate Joe O'Dea joins C&B to talk about his quest to flip a Senate seat.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
